	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64812393"><p>Canada banned single-use plastic bags at grocery checkouts a while back.  Now everybody brings reusable cloth bags or other reusable containers to the store.  It's really no big deal, and it does eliminate unsightly decaying plastic bags flapping randomly in trees and on fences.</p></div>
	</div>

